d to find out more about the Gradle plugin and maybe also look at other tests that are available. I’m curious about what resources are out there to help me understand it better. There’s probably documentation or examples I can reference. I want to ensure I'm getting accurate and helpful information. Let’s explore this together so I can provide the user with solid answers about Gradle plugins!\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_Jt9m8oMU3IGJI6AsvIVCSgxG|fc_024a35e51a7efdf0016a102a651c5481968f0f274d322c46a5", "name": "bash", "arguments": {"command": "rg \"java.security.manager|setSecurityManager|SecurityManager\" tests/src -n | head -100", "timeout": 10}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 38784, "output": 3070, "cacheRead": 7680, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 49534, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1779444272110, "responseId": "resp_024a35e51a7efdf0016a102a3106bc8196a5dace8fcb00a8ea"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_Jt9m8oMU3IGJI6AsvIVCSgxG|fc_024a35e51a7efdf0016a102a651c5481968f0f274d322c46a5", "toolName": "bash", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "tests/src/org.openjfx/javafx-base/13-ea/src/test/java/org_openjfx/javafx_base/MethodUtilTest.java:36:    void publicMethodsFastPathEnumeratesAccessibleMethodsWithoutSecurityManager() throws Exception {\ntests/src/org.jboss.resteasy/resteasy-client/6.2.12.Final/build.gradle:31:        jvmArgs += [\"-Djava.security.manager=allow\"]\ntests/src/org.jboss.resteasy/resteasy-client/6.2.12.Final/src/test/java/org_jboss_resteasy/resteasy_client/ClientProxyTest.java:22:    void defaultMethodInvocationUsesSpecialLookupWithoutSecurityManager() {\ntests/src/org.jboss.resteasy/resteasy-client/6.2.12.Final/src/test/java/org_jboss_resteasy/resteasy_client/ClientProxyTest.java:32:    void defaultMethodInvocationUsesPrivilegedSpecialLookupWithSecurityManager() {\ntes